# IRIS AI caregiver, has the ability to directly send emergency messages or make emergency calls using only voice commands, without the need for typing or dialing. 
- This feature allows for quick and hands-free access to emergency services, which can be especially helpful in situations where every second counts.
- With Iris, users can simply speak their emergency needs, and she will immediately send the necessary messages or make the calls to emergency services. 
- This innovative feature showcases Iris's advanced AI capabilities and her commitment to providing seamless and life-saving support to those in need.
